# python computation

Repository to learn numpy, scipy and sympy

## current status

- single_pendulm.py is code to develop sympy was of investigating stability of
non-linear system of ODEs around fixed points;

- for now it finds the fixed points, computes the Jacobian and can apply Hurwatz
criteria on the characteristics polynomial to figure out if the point is stable
or not

- todo is develop methods for testing Lypunov function candidates as explained

